/obj/item/paper{
	name = "Workshop control instructions";
	default_raw_text = "**Prison Workshop Guidelines**<br><br>In compliance with section 6-1 of the Intersystems agreement on prisoner rehabilitation, Nanotrasen is to provide amenities to convicts with the aim of rehabilitating them into society.<br><br>As such, we have fitted your station with an revolutionary workshop holodeck that will offer a space for convicts to work in exchange for reduced prison sentences.<br><br>So far there are two workshops, a donut assembly line, and a plushes sweatshop. You may change them at your leisure depending on the station needs.<br><br>We are aware of the security risks posed by this endeavour, as convicts will get access to tools that may prove detrimental to the stability of the prison. As such we have fitted your console with an **emergency shutdown** button that will unload the current workshop. Be aware that we are compelled by interstellar law to reload a random program after 2 minutes.<br><br>All items contained within the workshop will be unloaded once the program is changed, except for the goods the prisoners will have produced. Be aware that any items **taken out of the area** will not be unloaded by the console, as such it is your duty as warden to make sure that prisoners aren't stashing dangerous weapons inside the prison."
	},
